_sText:
This is just an alpha version of a map I want to make.  I am just testing the layout of the map first, and will texture it if I get a good response.  Please try it out and feel free to comment.  I mostly need layout suggestions at the moment, and will texture it nicely once this testing is done.

UPDATE!: (October 1, 2009): I have made a newer version of this map with nicer corners so it is less blocky like mentioned.  This was something that also was bugging me for a while so I decided to change it.  Othere than that it is all the same, this version has been uploaded.  (Images still from the previous version!)

I scrapped the idea to put side guards on the starting barrier.

UPDATE: (October 6, 2009): I am not sure if the newest version uploaded properly so I will reupload it now.

UPDATE: (October 8, 2009): Yesterday or the day before I started adding in textures and details, plus I added in an environmental light.  This will not be posted yet however, because not all of the texturing is very appealing at the moment.

UPDATE: (October 15, 2009): I have decided to release a textured version with basic lighting and details.  It will be coming soon, but for now I just replaced my last screenshot with a screenshot of the new map.  I will upload it soon!  I also may move buyzones up onto the map so it can be used for both gungame and other modes.

UPDATE: (October 31, 2009): Still tweaking with the newer version.  HAPPY HALLOWEEN!
